## üìä Success Metrics Checklist

### **After Day 1** (Foundation)
- [ ] Both containers running (`docker-compose ps` shows 2/2 up)
- [ ] GPU memory allocated (nvidia-smi shows 13-14GB of 16GB used)
- [ ] API responding (`curl http://localhost:8000/v1/models` works)
- [ ] No GPU errors in logs

### **After Day 2** (Integration)
- [ ] Research scripts functional (ai-research, ai-code, ai-write work)
- [ ] Model switcher working (30-90 second restart time)
- [ ] Logging system active (ai-interactions.jsonl growing)
- [ ] Baseline metrics documented

### **After Day 3** (Validation)
- [ ] Complete workflow tested (literature ‚Üí writing ‚Üí analysis)
- [ ] TTFT <50ms (aim for 20-30ms)
- [ ] Throughput >120 tok/s (aim for 140-170 tok/s)
- [ ] GPU utilization 85%+ (optimal memory usage)
- [ ] Model switch <60s (aim for 30s)
- [ ] Uptime 99%+ (no crashes during 8-hour test)
- [ ] Ready for production use

### **First Month**
- [ ] 30+ minutes daily productivity gain maintained
- [ ] No infrastructure overhead (5-10 min/day)
- [ ] All research workflows optimized
- [ ] Monthly power cost <$40
- [ ] Zero unplanned downtime

