## üéì Learning Outcomes

After completing this deployment, you'll understand:

1. **GPU vs. CPU Inference Tradeoffs** (speed vs. quality)
2. **Model Quantization** (FP8, Q4_K_M impact on performance)
3. **Docker Containerization** (practical single-container deployment)
4. **GPU Memory Management** (PagedAttention, KV cache optimization)
5. **Performance Benchmarking** (measuring TTFT, throughput)
6. **Infrastructure-as-Code** (reproducible deployments)
7. **Workflow Optimization** (automating research tasks)
8. **Cost Analysis** (comparing on-prem vs. cloud)

